01:52.430]Some fairytale bliss\n[01:54.820]Just something I can turn to\n[01:57.110]Somebody I can miss\n[01:59.190]I want something just like this\n[02:08.640]I want something just like this\n[02:17.490]Oh I want something just like this\n[02:20.170]Doo-doo-doo, doo-doo-doo\n[02:22.780]Doo-doo-doo, doo-doo\n[02:25.050]Doo-doo-doo, doo-doo-doo\n[02:27.100]Oh I want something just like this\n[02:29.810]Doo-doo-doo, doo-doo-doo\n[02:32.050]Doo-doo-doo, doo-doo\n[02:34.470]Doo-doo-doo, doo-doo-doo\n[02:37.270]Where'd you wanna go?\n[02:39.200]How much you wanna risk?\n[02:41.230]I'm not looking for somebody\n[02:43.550]With some superhuman gifts\n[02:46.120]Some superhero\n[02:48.320]Some fairytale bliss\n[02:50.720]Just something I can turn to\n[02:53.010]Somebody I can kiss\n[02:55.150]I want something just like this\n[03:13.640]Oh I want something just like this\n[03:32.360]Oh I want something just like this\n[03:50.950]Oh I want something just like this\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":35,"lyric":"[00:07.820]我曾饱览古老的书籍\n[00:10.140]那些传说与神话\n[00:12.280]阿喀琉斯和他的战利品\n[00:14.620]赫拉克勒斯与他的天赋神力\n[00:17.100]**侠的控制力\n[00:19.340]和蝙蝠侠的铁拳\n[00:22.310]显而易见我未能名列其中\n[00:26.070]她说，你想去何方？\n[00:28.700]你甘愿承担多大的风险？\n[00:30.700]我并不渴求\n[00:32.970]那些超人类的天赋\n[00:35.610]那种超级英雄\n[00:37.920]那些童话般的天赐之福\n[00:40.380]只是一些我能力所能及的事情\n[00:42.600]吻到我爱的人就好\n[00:44.670]我想要的仅此而已\n[00:47.350]\n[00:49.560]\n[00:51.880]\n[00:53.910]噢 我想要的仅此而已\n[00:56.560]\n[00:58.960]\n[01:01.240]\n[01:03.140]噢 我想要的仅此而已\n[01:12.770]我只想要这些\n[01:22.460]我曾饱览古老的书籍\n[01:24.630]那些传说与神话\n[01:26.880]他们所讲述的圣约\n[01:29.260]月亮的阴晴圆缺\n[01:31.580]还有超人展示\n[01:33.870]他飞天前的装束\n[01:37.290]但我不是这样的英雄\n[01:40.540]她说，你想去何方？\n[01:43.170]你能承担多大的风险？\n[01:45.240]我并不渴求\n[01:47.520]那些超人类的天赋\n[01:50.140]那种超级英雄\n[01:52.430]那些童话般的天赐之福\n[01:54.820]只是一些我能改变的\n[01:57.110]思念我爱的人\n[01:59.190]我想要的仅此而已\n[02:08.640]我想要的仅此而已\n[02:17.490]噢 我想要的仅此而已\n[02:20.170]\n[02:22.780]\n[02:25.050]\n[02:27.100]噢 我想要的仅此而已\n[02:29.810]\n[02:32.050]\n[02:34.470]\n[02:37.270]你想要到何方？\n[02:39.200]你能经受得住多少风险？\n[02:41.230]我并不渴求那些\n[02:43.550]超人类的天赋\n[02:46.120]那种超级英雄\n[02:48.320]那些童话般的天赐之福\n[02:50.720]只是一些我能力所能及的事情\n[02:53.010]吻到我爱的人就好\n[02:55.150]这就是我想要的\n[03:13.640]噢 我想要的仅此而已\n[03:32.360]噢 我想要的仅此而已\n[03:50.950]噢 我想要的仅此而已"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"yrc":{"version":37,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"制作人: \"},{\"tx\":\"The Chainsmokers\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Coldplay\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/6qlUiubUXhzk6VBwT8kkPQ==/109951170699828052.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=89365&type=artist\"}]}\n{\"t\":1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Guy Berryman\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/GFoWXND8bA70ybfGo2PHYw==/109951163678573711.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=203178&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Chris Martin\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/rnAH0jzukedQOKct8PBVvg==/18690598161409834.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=688269&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Jonny Buckland\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/tVvGsYMJj3Qna9peOoC0CQ==/109951164206792446.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=13055154&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Andrew Taggart\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/16lNqWY2XSubc3nlHYpfxg==/109951165953556553.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=13080339&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Will Champion\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/vFGPAFxQZo-e1DDlmH5e6Q==/109951164206807095.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=13121621&type=artist\"}]}\n{\"t\":2000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Guy Berryman\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/GFoWXND8bA70ybfGo2PHYw==/109951163678573711.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=203178&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Chris Martin\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/rnAH0jzukedQOKct8PBVvg==/18690598161409834.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=688269&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Jonny Buckland\",\"li\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/tVvGsYMJj3Qna9pe